Nixadoraz hirnnyodhonu hacho put. Kourou pamvancho dhonurvidhyentolo guru dronnachary hachekodden dhonurvidhea xokpakhatir ekolvy gel'lo. Ten'na to hin kullantolo asa oxem sangun dronncharean taka vidhea divpachem nhoikarolem. Eklavean dronnchareacho matyecho putllo kelo ani taka guru manun vhodd bhavartan dhonurvidhyecho svotach obheas kelo.

Hea prosongauporant, ekdam dronnachary kourou ani panddou hogea aplea xixeamvangodda ranant bhomvta astona tanchea vangdda ayil'lea kutreachem tondd sat bann marun konn tori bond kel'lem tankam dislem. Dhonurvidhyentolo to chomtkar polloun drinnchareasokott soglleank ozap zalem. Hi koramot ekolveachi axil'li. Dronncharean apnnak dhonurvidhea divpachem nhoikarolem, tori apnne taka guru manun dhonurvidhyechi sadhna keli ani hi vidhea prapt keli. Oxem sangun,taka aplo xixy nanun gheucho oxem dronnachareak ekolvean venoilem. Ekolveachi gurubhkti parkhupakhatir asumye, dronnacharean dhonurvidhyent samko gorjecho oso ujvea hatacho angttho gurudkxinna mhunn ekolveakodden maglo. Ekolvean rokhddoch to kapun dilo. Dhonurvidhyent orzunaporos ekolvy vhodd zait hea bhoyan ekolveacho angttho manlo ani ekuveacher vhodd onyai kelo, oso arop kaim zannakosun dronnachareacher zata. Kourou-panddou modlea bharti-i zhuzant ekolvy kourvanche votten panddou add zhujlo.

